# Authors and Contributors

This file contains the list of people who have contributed to the Qurox Post-Quantum Cryptography Library.

## Primary Author and Copyright Holder

**Philippe Lecrosnier** <lecro.philippe@icloud.com>
- Original author and creator
- Copyright holder (2026)
- Primary maintainer
- GitHub: @zxfae

## Contributors

To contribute to this project, please see CONTRIBUTING.md for guidelines.

By contributing to this project, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the Apache License 2.0, and you acknowledge that Philippe Lecrosnier retains copyright ownership of the overall project.

## Acknowledgments

This project builds upon the work of:
- NIST Post-Quantum Cryptography Standardization project
- The Rust cryptography ecosystem
- Apache Software Foundation for the licensing framework

For a complete list of dependencies and their authors, see Cargo.toml and the respective crate documentation.
